You have exceeded your premium request allowance. We have automatically switched you to GPT-4.1 which is included with your plan. [Enable additional paid premium requests](command:chat.enablePremiumOverages) to continue using premium models.```seqdiag
actor User
boundary AccountDetailPage
control AccountController
participant ":AccountService" as AccountService
participant ":AccountModel" as AccountModel
database Database

User->AccountDetailPage: 1. Click view account detail
activate AccountDetailPage
activate User

AccountDetailPage->AccountController: 2. GET /accounts/{id}
activate AccountController

AccountController->AccountService: 3. Get account detail by ID
activate AccountService

AccountService->AccountModel: 4. Find account by ID
activate AccountModel

AccountModel->Database: 5. Retrieve account data by ID
activate Database
Database-->AccountModel: 6. Result (account data or null)
deactivate Database

AccountModel-->AccountService: 7. Return account entity or not found
deactivate AccountModel

alt Account not found
    AccountService-->AccountController: 8.1. Return not found result
    AccountController-->AccountDetailPage: 8.1.1. Return 404 Not Found + message
    AccountDetailPage-->User: 8.1.2. Show error: "Account not found"
else Account exists
    AccountService-->AccountController: 8.2. Return AccountDetailResponse
    deactivate AccountService
    AccountController-->AccountDetailPage: 8.2.1. Return 200 OK + account data
    deactivate AccountController
    AccountDetailPage-->User: 8.2.2. Display result 

end

deactivate AccountDetailPage
deactivate User
```